{"sn22.22:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 22.22 ","sn22.22:0.2":"3. Bharavagga ","sn22.22:0.3":"Bharasutta ","sn22.22:1.1":"Savatthiyam … tatra kho … ","sn22.22:1.2":"“bharanca vo, bhikkhave, desessami bharaharanca bharadananca bharanikkhepananca. ","sn22.22:1.3":"Tam sunatha. ","sn22.22:1.4":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, bharo? ","sn22.22:1.5":"Pancupadanakkhandha tissa vacaniyam. ","sn22.22:1.6":"Katame panca? ","sn22.22:1.7":"Rupupadanakkhandho, vedanupadanakkhandho, sannupadanakkhandho, sankharupadanakkhandho, vinnanupadanakkhandho; ","sn22.22:1.8":"ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, bharo. ","sn22.22:2.1":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, bharaharo? ","sn22.22:2.2":"Puggalo tissa vacaniyam. ","sn22.22:2.3":"Yvayam ayasma evamnamo evangotto; ","sn22.22:2.4":"ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, bharaharo. ","sn22.22:3.1":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, bharadanam? ","sn22.22:3.2":"Yayam tanha ponobhavika nandiragasahagata tatratatrabhinandini, seyyathidam—","sn22.22:3.3":"kamatanha, bhavatanha, vibhavatanha. ","sn22.22:3.4":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, bharadanam. ","sn22.22:4.1":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, bharanikkhepanam? ","sn22.22:4.2":"Yo tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodho cago patinissaggo mutti analayo. ","sn22.22:4.3":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, bharanikkhepanan”ti. ","sn22.22:5.1":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","sn22.22:5.2":"Idam vatvana sugato athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","sn22.22:6.1":"“Bhara have pancakkhandha, ","sn22.22:6.2":"bharaharo ca puggalo; ","sn22.22:6.3":"Bharadanam dukham loke, ","sn22.22:6.4":"bharanikkhepanam sukham. ","sn22.22:7.1":"Nikkhipitva garum bharam, ","sn22.22:7.2":"annam bharam anadiya; ","sn22.22:7.3":"Samulam tanhamabbuyha, ","sn22.22:7.4":"nicchato parinibbuto”ti. ","sn22.22:7.5":"Pathamam. "}